US: Repetition is the Mother of Wisdom
It’s comic that Barack Obama, the president with the smartest man’s reputation, as a diligent student repeated the Afghan matter of his predecessor’s strategy, which he himself took for the foolishest.
When he finally revealed his long-awaited Afghan approach, it was shown to be a copy of the script used for Iraq by Bush, created three years ago.
