The name "Tawa" comes from the sun god of the Hopi Indians.
For Sterling Nesbitt is an exceptional find: "Dinosaur fossils of the Trias are extremely rare, usually only individual fragments are found."
Other dinosaurs experts don’t share all such enthusiasm.
This finding is not particularly spectacular, but confirms some theories about the ancient history of the dinosaurs, says Martin Sander from the University of Bonn, for example.
According to the current opinion stream, dinosaurs first appeared about 230 million years ago.
